{"tid":2018111,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日第一日返郵差送信","createTime":"2020-05-15T12:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T14:49:56.000Z","uid":223432,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"92575644ba45736ee3b6bd68a585fe31577b2606","tid":2018111,"uid":223432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:08:18.000Z","msg":"之前從來未孭過郵差個袋，第一轉就有8棟樓，頂硬上，係就係慢小小，送完一轉，手已經好硬，第二轉8棟已經手軟，行唔到咁，師兄睇量我，俾我6棟先，勉強頂到，好不容易先捱到中午飯，去左沙田一間茶餐廳到食，咁送左舒湯黎，攞起隻匙羹，我屌，提唔能起，右手已經硬能曬，我要用個頭壓低黎飲湯，心諗，仆街喇，重有半日點捱，好，食完飯，又送過，又熱又曬，已經出到沒曬汗，我知再唔飲水，一定會死，我愉雞經過7-11買支野飲，一嘢飲曬都唔夠，但起碼有返汗出，到放工時，佢地問我返唔返第二日，我話唔返，第日就辭職，好敬佩佢地，份工真係唔簡單"},{"pid":"39f7fb82675e980aeee29fa3eb296701b69a5c67","tid":2018111,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:09:17.000Z","msg":"公墓猿都唔做？"},{"pid":"592517da92ceec5199689f9b43e41558688771a2","tid":2018111,"uid":223432,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ppqMJ6i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FppqMJ6i.jpg&h=bc0177cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係唔好睇小個袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入面啲信多到仆街重撚死"},{"pid":"d00fc2c9bc69a4a4d5d88bbcdc7d43a45ecb37c5","tid":2018111,"uid":248670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:12:02.000Z","msg":"咁辛苦考完唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8243367feed497fa66c0d7604bbdd8b4b8f280a5","tid":2018111,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:19:27.000Z","msg":"仲要比狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85be17024f61f2ec9d9a650a5dec85cac083805","tid":2018111,"uid":32150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14420abbfebe3c1c8a053bfc5a476a18de96dc3","tid":2018111,"uid":101265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:53:23.000Z","msg":"同送水篇文一樣既<br />\n<br />\n0分重作啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93878f377457db1472c25b1cdb72cb95b0885621","tid":2018111,"uid":304228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c14420abbfebe3c1c8a053bfc5a476a18de96dc3","tid":2018111,"uid":101265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:53:23.000Z","msg":"同送水篇文一樣既<br />\n<br />\n0分重作啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:49:56.000Z","msg":"同紮鐵篇文一樣"}]}